{"tid":106734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五年前, 有一舊臭既屎, 一舊唔臭既屎, 一舊多士比你簡","createTime":"2017-02-04T02:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T02:48:19.000Z","uid":2023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19c518f1b112dae7ccd230f907987eba37e18330","tid":106734,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"但其實唔到你簡食邊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你知道你無可能食到個舊多士...<br />\n吃不到的葡萄是酸的, 所以你用好多理論批評舊多士<br />\n<br />\n佢無能力令我飽囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊多士睇落唔多好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我係無可能食到塊多士, 但我根本唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  so WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後你就開始諗下舊唔臭既屎有咩好, 因為佢係你有可能食到既最佳選項。<br />\n<br />\n佢睇落似屎姐, 可能佢係一舊朱古力黎!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都似wooo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 可能仲係吉百利朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定係啦, 我地要爭取食朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n............<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日: 有四舊屎擺係眼前.... 大家都討論緊邊舊屎無咁臭, 邊舊有可能係朱古力, 但已經無人記得....<br />\n其實佢地可以爭取下叫廚房整番舊多士...."},{"pid":"d4ad3341b380eefe3393f4ebdc8133fbedbaac68","tid":106734,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"廚房d人咁惡 四年前塞曬係門口抗議都比廚房佬打散曬 仲可以點抗議爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沖入廚房同佢死過咩 不如轉地方食d人食既野好過啦"},{"pid":"c55a37f9d77d645a1c61be6da301140bc9850fca","tid":106734,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"我唔會求廚房整多士<br />\n因為整左我都冇得食<br />\n反正我講咩廚房都唔會聽<br />\n<br />\n但都唔會去理邊舊屎冇咁臭<br />\n因為都唔到我揀，又一定要硬食，同始終都係屎<br />\n眼見身邊好多本身想食多士嘅人<br />\n竟然好熱衷於討論邊舊屎冇咁臭<br />\n真係好唏噓<br />\n<br />\n我關注嘅唔係食咩屎<br />\n而係點解我冇得揀！"},{"pid":"4f3d5edd693428af76b27e689adfca22fcb7b932","tid":106734,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"仲要比錢食一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}